cryptopunks.Description: CryptoPunks are 10,000 unique collectible characters with proof of ownership stored on the Ethereum blockchain. They are one of the earliest examples of a "Non-Fungible Token" on Ethereum, and were inspiration for the ERC-721 standard that powers most digital art and collectibles.

old-contract.Description: Contracts/addresses which are migrating or have migrated to a new contract/address. This includes token swaps as well.
